#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.84"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.84:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.84:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga"
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Adhikaraṇasamathasutta"
msgstr "84. Settlement of Disciplinary Issues"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.144"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.84:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattime, bhikkhave, adhikaraṇasamathā dhammā uppannuppannānaṃ adhikaraṇānaṃ "
"samathāya vūpasamāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these seven principles for the settlement of any "
"disciplinary issues that might arise."

msgctxt "an7.84:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

#. VAR: paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ dātabbaṃ, yebhuyyasikā dātabbā, tassapāpiyasikā dātabbā, tiṇavatthārako dātabbo → paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ, yebhuyyasikā, tassa pāpiyasikā, tiṇavatthārako (syā1-3) 2V:2094 vinayena ca 8D:1021 saṅgītisuttena ca
msgctxt "an7.84:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammukhāvinayo dātabbo, sativinayo dātabbo, amūḷhavinayo dātabbo, "
"paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ dātabbaṃ, yebhuyyasikā dātabbā, tassapāpiyasikā dātabbā, "
"tiṇavatthārako dātabbo."
msgstr ""
"Removal in the presence of those concerned is applicable. Removal by "
"accurate recollection is applicable. Removal due to recovery from madness is "
"applicable. The acknowledgement of the offense is applicable. The decision "
"of a majority is applicable. A verdict of aggravated misconduct is "
"applicable. Covering over with grass is applicable."

msgctxt "an7.84:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta adhikaraṇasamathā dhammā uppannuppannānaṃ "
"adhikaraṇānaṃ samathāya vūpasamāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the seven principles for the settlement of any disciplinary issues "
"that might arise.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.84:1.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.84:1.6"
msgid "Vinayavaggo aṭṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.1"
msgid "Caturo vinayadharā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.2"
msgid "caturo ceva sobhanā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.3"
msgid "Sāsanaṃ adhikaraṇa—​"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.84:2.4"
msgid "samathenaṭṭhame dasāti."
msgstr ""
